data.description: Welcome to this beautiful El Dorado Estates 2-story pool home, perfect for entertaining!  Originally a 5 bedroom, the 5th bedroom has been joined to the primary bedroom to create a large en suite bedroom complete with fireplace and balcony access.  Upon entering through the reception foyer you will notice views all the way through the house and to the pool.  This home has a downstairs bedroom and bath for those needing a first floor option.  The living room is huge with a fireplace and access to the patio and pool area.  There is a large formal dining room also with access to the patio and pool area.  The kitchen has a nook area and is bright and sunny with stainless appointments.  The family room is being used as a game room and has so many possibilities, also with sliding door access to the side of the house, a wet bar, and direct garage access.  Upstairs you will find a total of 3 bedrooms.  Besides the primary bedroom there are two other nice bedrooms with closet walls and access to the hall bath.  You will enjoy newer windows, fresh paint, forced air heat and central a/c, and recessed lighting just to name a few upgrades.  Located near an award winning school and close to El Dorado Park where you can enjoy all kinds of activities year round!
